Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:03.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:04.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.31,0:00:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The S Class Wizard Advancement \NExam has finally started!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:11.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Erza and Mira passed this exam to \Nbecome S Class Wizards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:13.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the first test finished, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:17.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:19.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what was the second test again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was searching for the \Nfounding Master, Mavis's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:26.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But a weirdo went and barged in on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:28.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gettin' in the way \Nof the exam, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:15.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Erza-san... What \Nkind of magic does Mest-san use?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:17.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah yes, I suppose you aren't yet aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:21.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mest uses... Uh, that! You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know either, Erza-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:30.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean that Mest might \Nnot be a member of the guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:34.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a hunch at first. \NBut the strange thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:39.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the more doubts I have, the more \Nclear my knowledge of Mest becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:43.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't follow you in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:45.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:50.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The knowledge I have of him, even \Nthough I just joined the guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Mest Gryder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:56.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the disciple of Mystogan, the Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:03:01.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was chosen to take the S Class Exam \Nlast year, but unfortunately failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:04.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:07.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Any other information on \Nhim is cloudy and vague...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:11.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See why I told her not to \Npartner with that weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:15.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we must hurry! \NWendy might be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:18.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen this kind of flower before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mest-san, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:28.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know! I want to know what \Nthese strange flowers taste like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:31.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't eat the flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:36.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsu... Aren't we heading to the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I ain't gonna be satisfied \Nuntil I give that bastard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:43.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,who did this to Igneel's \Nscarf a taste of my fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:46.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So...  You're gonna search for the grave \Nwhile also searching for that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just choose one or the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do both at once, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Natsu for you, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:59.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people after?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:05.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To hunt the fairies here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.30,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Thundering Roar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:11.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul of Iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a racket!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:17.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic from letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same magic as yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:22.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Levy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:26.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic is Eastern Solid Script!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:28.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:41.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Egg Buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:57.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... I can't hear his \Nsteps with all the noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:07.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Solid Script: Silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The noise has gone back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your writing cancel out mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:20.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:26.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.97,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Zuzazazazazazaza
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.31,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Slash
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:42.52,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Supepepepepepe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:50.99,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Slash-Slash
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... This is messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:13.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:15.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:28.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's cutting my iron scales \Nlike they're nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:25.61,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Go
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.32,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Bi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:27.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Ba
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:27.78,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:28.57,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Za
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.11,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Zan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.70,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Stab
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stab!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.29,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasha
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:43.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:45.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crying Bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:51.72,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Zan-zan-zan-zan-zan-zan-zan-zan-zan... Zan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:55.56,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaki
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:01.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:06.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:09.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're all as weak as these two,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:12.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we can finish them all off \Nbefore the main force arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Main force, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's still alive-peron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:27.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The main force is the full might \Nof our Guild, Grimoire Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy, escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't just some war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be way bigger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and tell everyone about \Nthis, on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:46.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle these chumps fine on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:53.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing? Hurry and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:14.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you... Letting that woman get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:18.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever-peron... Just makes \Nthe hunt more fun-peron.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:26.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An all-out war against Fairy Tail, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:28.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:32.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reminds me of back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:38.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you that picking a fight \Nwith Fairy Tail was a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:41.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:46.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna taste the same fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:52.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The full force of Grimoire \NHeart is coming to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to tell everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something terrible is happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:18.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:23.75,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Block
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:30.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, look above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy Egg Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.52,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Shubabababababa
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:55.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think my forged iron is going \Nto lose to that rusty blade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.33,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Stab-stab-stab-stab
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:08.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stab!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:11.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're open!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:29.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:41.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy... Levy... Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get those injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:49.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, Juvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got trouble! Gajeel is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:10.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Making an enemy of Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:14.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are the same as I was back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:20.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel was once part of another guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:22.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Its name was Phantom Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:28.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They kidnapped Lucy, and drove \NFairy Tail into a corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:32.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but were completely defeated \Nand Phantom Lord was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:39.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their various wizards all set out \Nand went their separate ways, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:57.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Makarov!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:02.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:06.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:08.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For a little talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:16.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia entered my guild the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:21.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and she's pretty worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that rain woman thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:33.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:36.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me. I ain't decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:38.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll get by somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:53.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking when \Nyou picked a fight with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:58.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Phantom Lord mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:01.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did the guild mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did being a wizard mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:11.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:13.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:20.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking what do you, yourself, \Nthink about who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:26.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you have taken people's \Nlives if Jose had ordered you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:29.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that unquestioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:33.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, that's no different \Nthan being a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:38.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think you're \Nas boring a man as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:41.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up already. Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:46.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to throw \Nyourself into the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:50.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Wanna join my guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:54.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people in this \Nworld who prefer solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:01.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is no one who can withstand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:10.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who destroyed your guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put all that aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:17.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And... I hurt your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:23.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:26.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will never forgive, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:32.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I ignored a young man trying \Nto throw himself into the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:35.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be myself I could never forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:47.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't me saving you. I'm simply \Nshowing you the path to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:53.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go forward, or will you \Nstop? It's up to you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:15.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:21.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Wizard!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:28.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My katana!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:31.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:42.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Dragon Slayer Art!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.31,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Hi~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:01.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Karma Demon:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:06.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron God Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:39.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:41.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel! Hang in there, Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:55.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I could handle 'em by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:09.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The main force will be here any moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:13.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wizards far out of my league are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seven Kin of Purgatory!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven Kin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:24.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm halting the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:28.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, deploy for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:32.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Condition red! Prepare to intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On this island? That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A red signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:49.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:52.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the exam? Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:54.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called off for now, with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:59.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that guy from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:07.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... That's a signal that \Nmeans an enemy is coming to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:09.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're closing in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:12.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who or what they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:14.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but they think they can pick a fight with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn the tables on 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:17.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:27.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my final exam! Even though \NI wish to drop out of the guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:30.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me! \NI'm continuing the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Cana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:37.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray! Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:42.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the two of you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:43.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were foll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:46.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We just happened upon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:48.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:52.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy is coming... This \Nis no time for exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head to the emergency gathering area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough information now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:02.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen? Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san, what should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's search for Mest and Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:16.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible they're lost and \Ndon't know where the camp is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take Gajeel to the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:20.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:24.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A shrimp like you shouldn't push herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:27.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure talk big for a \Nguy who can't stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:30.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:34.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia wants to see Gray-sama very soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:40.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's hear what you're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd talk to the likes of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:49.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:52.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary Black Wizard Zeref!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref is here on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:57.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:00.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref lived hundreds of years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,400 years, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it! There's \Nno way he's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:09.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:19.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive! He's been alive \Nthese past 400 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:28.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Master Hades says that \Nhe's currently "sleeping".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:35.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Zeref awakens,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:39.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,this world will be bathed in pure darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:44.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! This \Nis Fairy Tail holy ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:48.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me you plan to run rampant \Non this divinely protected Fairy island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:53.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Hade's personal \Nguard will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:58.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd do well not to underestimate \Nthe 7 Kin of Purgatory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:02.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wizard of time, Ultear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:05.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rustyrose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss, Caprico-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kain Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:13.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zancrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:15.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:20.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the final one is \Nalready on this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:23.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:30.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mest-san, what does that \Nsignal flare mean again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:34.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:38.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know! I seriously want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:41.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've forgotten too, Mest-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:46.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And besides, Mest-san... You really \Nshouldn't try to put everything in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:45.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... Should I make my \Nmove before the main forces come?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:48.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:51.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla! Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:54.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:58.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mest!  Who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:01.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:03.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mystogan's disciple, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:09.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan would not have taken \Non a disciple in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:14.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well choosing to use a human \Nwho is no longer in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but your cover story was too weak, \NMest. If that's your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:21.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.17,0:24:00.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa! A bunch of guys \NI dunno are comin' here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:03.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That mark... Could they be Grimoire Heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:05.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would a Dark Guild be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:07.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is also part of the S Class exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:09.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a big festival, testing our strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.41,0:24:10.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty weird festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:13.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, we've gone from exams to festivals?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Makarov's Charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:18.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not a festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.90,0:24:20.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess they're enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.36,0:24:21.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That means I can blast 'em, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.87,0:24:24.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But try not to get blasted yourself, 'kay?
